%% Trace: features/01-刪除帳戶.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Ctrl as AccountLifecycleController
    participant Auth as JwtAuthGuard
    participant Svc as AccountDeletionService
    participant BioRepo as BiometricDeviceTokenRepository
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,FE: 使用者已登入 (Bearer token)
    User->>FE: 帳號設定 → 刪除帳戶
    FE-->>User: 警告彈窗「刪除後無法恢復」(BR-43)
    User->>FE: 確認 + 輸入密碼
    FE->>Ctrl: DELETE /account (password, confirmation_acknowledged=true) [Bearer]
    Ctrl->>Auth: validateJwt
    Auth-->>Ctrl: currentUserId
    Ctrl->>Svc: deleteSelf(currentUserId, password, confirmation_acknowledged)
    Svc->>Svc: assertConfirmed(confirmation_acknowledged)
    Svc->>Repo: findById(currentUserId)
    Repo-->>Svc: member_auth
    Svc->>Svc: verifyHash(password, password_hash) - BR-38
    Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET is_deleted=true, deleted_at=now()
    Svc->>BioRepo: revokeAllByMemberAuthId(currentUserId, reason='account_deleted')
    BioRepo->>DB: UPDATE biometric_device_tokens SET is_revoked=true (CLARIFY-06)
    Note over Svc: CRM Customer/積分/優惠券保留不刪 (BR-40)
    Svc-->>Ctrl: deleted
    Ctrl-->>FE: 204 No Content
    FE->>FE: 清除 access_token (BR-41)
    FE-->>User: 導向登入頁
